{
  "stem": "13817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "You saw the people in there all in rags.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "When we were in there, we found out what happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The people in rags were the Polish Jews which were put into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The city was large.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The German called it Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Already in '39, and they lived there already two years or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the living conditions were just horrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "The streets were just, just dirt and mud, and and there were open sewers running through it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And you-- we didn't know what was hitting us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We were the second transport from Cologne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "The other one went about 10, 14 days early.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "With all the rest, we emptied an area in the slum area in this so-called ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And arriving every days were the transport of 1,000 each, two or three transports.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And they were pushed into this overpopulated area, which was overpopulated already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They pushed in there within, I think, within about a space of a month, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "There were all of a sudden 20,000 people. 20 more thousand people pushed into this overcrowded area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a lot of the Polish Jews spoke-- excuse me-- spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yiddish is a-- is a middle-aged German, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if they spoke slow, and a few spoke-- some of the German Jews spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A few of them spoke German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you would be able to communicate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was no communication there, because all of a sudden there was, on one side, they came in, these people out of a-- of a normal lifestyle, more or less, even, even deprived in Germany.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But still you lived a normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
